## All three path types side by side:
```
Top-down          Bottom-up         Node-to-node (LCA)
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
preorder          postorder         postorder + global tracker
info via params   info via return   info via return + joined at LCA
parent → child    child → parent    child → parent, joined at LCA
no global needed  no global needed  NEEDS global variable
void/bool         returns value     returns ONE side, tracks BOTH
```

